OL,3,C'Much-loved sister and aunt' killed in
OL,4,Ctaxi crash in Bradford
OL,6,FA woman, who died after the taxi she
OL,7,Fwas travelling in crashed, has been
OL,8,Fnamed by police.
OL,10,FDelia Sheridan, aged 71, died after
OL,11,Fthe taxi she was a passenger in was
OL,12,Fcrashed into a tree at around 10.17am
OL,13,Fon Saturday, 11 April.
OL,15,FThe driver of the grey Toyota Pirus
OL,16,Ftaxi, a man aged 72, was arrested at
OL,17,Fthe scene on suspicion causing death
OL,18,Fby dangerous driving. He was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital where he remains in a serious
OL,20,Fcondition.
