OL,3,C'Much-loved sister and aunt' killed in
OL,4,Ctaxi crash in Bradford
OL,6,FDelia's family have said: "A much-
OL,7,Floved sister and aunt, taken away too
OL,8,Fsoon. She will be sadly missed by the
OL,9,Ffamily."
OL,11,FHumberside Police have said: "Officers
OL,12,Ffrom the Major Collision Enquiry team
OL,13,Fare continuing to appeal for witnesses
OL,14,Fto the collision or who may have dash
OL,15,Fcam footage to come forward."
